{"tid":444112,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺留言有得正負評既介面設計係令人變弱智","createTime":"2017-10-22T08:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T10:25:57.000Z","uid":56498,"like":11,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7cf2f1ebecefc2a899c65f348519120f3de55e2","tid":444112,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"直接令人覺得多正評就岩，就有好既印象<br />\n所以啲人專揀多正評既黎睇,仲有埋熱門回覆<br />\n啲人變到唔撚洗用腦<br />\n<br />\n有負評就唔洗睇，唔洗諗，有人無端白事掉個負評，之後成班人跟住一齊比負評<br />\n<br />\n主導左第一印象同觀感<br />\n成件事變到fb ig化<br />\n<br />\n非主流意見同相反意見就沉底<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一個主張自由開放既討論區咁樣太弱智<br />\n<br />\n主題可以有，留言整翻走會唔會好啲<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"43885800ec768f475e7c7429f690d5244b85e0ee","tid":444112,"uid":56498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"淨係5毛可以利用黎刷主流意見呢個缺點就足夠捨棄呢個系統"},{"pid":"678e2de80f3c0ce0edcae762bba34350468b0ab8","tid":444112,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"仲有啲乞人憎既語殘有野唔好好講，擺低個正負評就走鳩左"},{"pid":"170e2d72e6838d83dafad2fcede32bf9b86c2232","tid":444112,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"（笑）"},{"pid":"49d36c241004854b36342498a9ecb0c656b1a009","tid":444112,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:53:25.000Z","msg":"由唔知幾時開始原來好多人都淨係睇熱門<br />\n我就知好多人根本冇用腦上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4ef7533c141768f58595d949b678b710d61b59","tid":444112,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:58:51.000Z","msg":"正負評唔岩係中小學forum度用"},{"pid":"3531a9868216d4ab03ba3d2fde838784d9469f1b","tid":444112,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"唔撚識批判思考？"},{"pid":"0bfd5b6e0551ab5a82c395b5417979df0e84048c","tid":444112,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:23:16.000Z","msg":"